|[.sup]2[/]|            |            |            |            |            | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Area of cov-|20,000      |83,230      |            |40,000      |26,570      | 
|ered buildi-|            |            |            |            |            | 
|ngs, m[.sup]2|            |            |            |            |            | 
|[/]      |            |            |            |            |            | 
